### Create supplier
POST http://localhost:8087/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Supplier SPA",
  "email": "contact@newsupplier.cl",
  "phone": "+56229998888",
  "address": "Av. New 123"
}

### Create supplier with duplicate email (should return 409)
POST http://localhost:8087/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Another Supplier",
  "email": "contact@newsupplier.cl"
}

### Create invalid supplier (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8087/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### List suppliers
GET http://localhost:8087/suppliers

### Get supplier by id
GET http://localhost:8087/suppliers/1

### Get non-existent supplier (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8087/suppliers/999

### Update supplier
PUT http://localhost:8087/suppliers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TecnoParts Distribution Updated",
  "email": "contact@tecnoparts.cl",
  "phone": "+56221111111",
  "address": "New address 456"
}

### Deactivate supplier (should return 204)
DELETE http://localhost:8087/suppliers/5

### Swagger UI
GET http://localhost:8087/swagger-ui.html
